scripts.build: npm run build:cjs && npm run build:esm && node -e "const https=require('https'),fs=require('fs');const download=(f)=>new Promise((res,rej)=>https.get('https://docs.agentmail.to/'+f,r=>r.pipe(fs.createWriteStream('dist/'+f)).on('finish',res).on('error',rej)));Promise.all(['llms.txt','llms-full.txt'].map(download)).catch(e=>{console.error(e);process.exit(1)});"
